sWeekFrom, to: currentDate\n  - \"last month\" → from: 28 days before thisWeekFrom, to: currentDate\n  - \"last quarter\" / \"last 3 months\" → from: 12 weeks before thisWeekFrom, to: currentDate\n  - No time reference → null (search all time for pattern/trend questions)\n- keywords: 2-5 key terms for the topic (exclude stop words)\n\n## Examples (assuming currentDate=2026-03-26, lastWeekFrom=2026-03-16, lastWeekTo=2026-03-22, thisWeekFrom=2026-03-23):\n\nQuestion: \"What did the team commit to last week?\"\n{\"intent\":\"status_query\",\"userFilter\":\"team\",\"entityTypes\":[\"commit\",\"plan_summary\"],\"timeRange\":{\"from\":\"2026-03-16\",\"to\":\"2026-03-22\"},\"keywords\":[\"commit\",\"last week\",\"team\"]}\n\nQuestion: \"What are the recurring carry-forward patterns?\"\n{\"intent\":\"carry_forward_query\",\"userFilter\":\"team\",\"entityTypes\":[\"carry_forward\",\"commit\"],\"timeRange\":null,\"keywords\":[\"carry-forward\",\"recurring\",\"patterns\"]}\n\nQuestion: \"Which KING/QUEEN work was achieved last week?\"\n{\"intent\":\"status_query\",\"userFilter\":\"team\",\"entityTypes\":[\"commit\"],\"timeRange\":{\"from\":\"2026-03-16\",\"to\":\"2026-03-22\"},\"keywords\":[\"KING\",\"QUEEN\",\"achieved\",\"last week\"]}\n\nQuestion: \"What did Alice work on this month?\"\n{\"intent\":\"status_query\",\"userFilter\":null,\"entityTypes\":[\"commit\",\"plan_summary\"],\"timeRange\":{\"from\":\"2026-02-23\",\"to\":\"2026-03-26\"},\"keywords\":[\"Alice\",\"work\",\"month\"]}\n\nQuestion: \"What scope changes happened recently?\"\n{\"intent\":\"scope_change_query\",\"userFilter\":\"team\",\"entityTypes\":[\"scope_change\"],\"timeRange\":{\"from\":\"2026-03-16\",\"to\":\"2026-03-26\"},\"keywords\":[\"scope\",\"changes\",\"recent\"]}\n\nRespond with ONLY a JSON object (no markdown fences):\n{\n  \"intent\": \"status_query|risk_query|carry_forward_query|plan_summary_query|ticket_query|scope_change_query|general_query\",\n  \"userFilter\": \"self|team|null\",\n  \"entityTypes\": [\"one to three entity types\"],\n  \"timeRange\": { \"from\": \"YYYY-MM-DD\", \"to\": \"YYYY-MM-DD\" },\n  \"keywords\": [\"key\", \"terms\"]\n}\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774823694169}}
